{"tid":647465,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【諗唔到會舊】世界盃主題曲被批老餅 譚詠麟：佢哋識唔識聽音樂？","createTime":"2018-04-30T00:38:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T20:37:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"fb61dcf9531561bc5a43f4ace30ebc930a802946","tid":647465,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:38:08.000Z","msg":"譚詠麟今日喺九龍灣出席新碟工作坊，佢將會喺30多位音樂人提供嘅作品中挑選適合歌曲收錄於即將推出嘅全新唱片當中，校長話：「今次令我好大壓力，因為太多好作品，喺30首入面忍心篩走只得3首。」校長仲表示已經聽咗五日，感覺歌曲水平好高。<br />\n<br />\n校長將會主唱世界盃主題曲《我們的夢》，不過就被網友批評似80年代歌曲，校長表示同創作人用咗近五日時間聽100首東歐民族歌曲做參考：「我哋將民族曲風變成時代曲，再加Rap，點會舊？諗都諗到唔會舊，佢哋識唔識聽音樂？」為咗令歌曲做到嘉年華會嘅感覺，再加上接觸過其他地方嘅世界盃歌曲，校長話最終決定唔用民族曲風，而係從蘇聯民族舞取靈感：「做流行曲易，但要混合民族曲風就好難。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180429/large/1524993827_437e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180429%2Flarge%2F1524993827_437e.jpg&h=ee67f610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180429/58132967?_ga=2.16049654.1504338981.1524884862-1567888096.1524463134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180429%2F58132967%3F_ga%3D2.16049654.1504338981.1524884862-1567888096.1524463134&d=iasvbpCkUkVJl2lTLqQ2pBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=73ad655c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180429%2F58132967%3F_ga%3D2.16049654.1504338981.1524884862-1567888096.1524463134&h=91580fe0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180429/58132967?_ga=2.16049654.1504338981.1524884862-1567888096.1524463134</a>"},{"pid":"5a57946492c16b5d068242421d8e1f69f6fc129e","tid":647465,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:40:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JsR0RUM0k0I\" da